{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/linux/if-not-weston","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>My fisrt problem was: <a href=\"/blog/center-window-in-weston\">How to center window in Weston?</a>. My second problem was: <a href=\"/linux/drop-shadow-in-weston\">Drop shadow effect in Weston</a></p>\n<p>The last one is so simple, but I didn't find a working solution. So</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Think twice before abandoning Xorg. <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayland_(display_server_protocol)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Wayland</a> breaks everything! <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/probonopd/9feb7c20257af5dd915e3a9f2d1f2277\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://gist.github.com/probonopd/9feb7c20257af5dd915e3a9f2d1f2277</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>I have stopped reading Weston's bug tracker on page 8 <a href=\"https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/wayland/weston/-/issues?page=8&#x26;state=opened\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/wayland/weston/-/issues?page=8&#x26;state=opened</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"alternatives\" style=\"position:relative;\">Alternatives<a href=\"#alternatives\" aria-label=\"alternatives permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Some alternatives I found</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\